  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're trapped in the dark with a killer psychopath. You must escape by solving clues, unlocking doors and completing puzzles. You only have 5 lives! Dominate your killer in random generated levels. Earn points by completing tasks and use them to unlock new killers. Move stealthily to avoid being hunted. Try the new story mode and escape your way to the very end. Take your chance at survival in this thrilling hide-and-seek horror game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929570/extras/a9d4355b130381bc75303b7bd697ecc1.poster.avif?t=1765410698\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929570/extras/a9d4355b130381bc75303b7bd697ecc1.webm?t=1765410698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929570/extras/a9d4355b130381bc75303b7bd697ecc1.mp4?t=1765410698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealthy Mechanics</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killer Customization</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story & Trial Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Generated Levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scary Encounters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrilling Gameplay</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve Puzzles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get Rewarded</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open Secret Rooms</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Permanent Death!</p></li></ul>",
